            <span class="block text-[#F5521A] mt-2">on Both Platforms</span>
          </h1>

          <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-800/95 font-medium leading-relaxed">
              A photographer portfolio. 12 pages. Image gallery, blog CMS, contact form, smooth animations. <strong>I built it on Framer. Then I built the exact same site on Webflow.</strong>
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-800/95 font-medium leading-relaxed mt-4">
              Here's what happened, hour by hour.
            </p>
          </div>

