              <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1">
                <li>‚Ä¢ Mobile responsive tweaks (2 hours)</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ SEO optimization (1 hour)</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Final testing (1 hour)</li>
