                  <span class="text-2xl font-black text-[#F5521A]">98/100</span>
                  <span class="text-gray-600">/ Framer</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Mobile: 98, Desktop: 96. Exceptional performance out of the box.</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
