                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Mobile: 82, Desktop: 85. Good but requires optimization.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-4 bg-green-50 border-l-4 border-green-500 p-4">
              <p class="text-sm text-green-900"><strong>Winner:</strong> Framer. Better optimization by default. Webflow requires manual tuning for similar scores.</p>
            </div>
